OL,3,CMigrant rescued from small boat says
OL,4,Csmugglers made him 'scared for his
OL,5,Clife'
OL,7,FAn asylum seeker rescued from the sea
OL,8,Fwhile he was travelling in a small
OL,9,Fboat said he was "afraid and scared
OL,10,Ffor his life" by people smugglers.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Hamza, whose
OL,13,Fname has been changed to protect his
OL,14,Fidentity after he fled persecution
OL,15,Ffrom the Taliban in Afghanistan, was
OL,16,Frescued alongside 38 others when their
OL,17,Frubber dinghy capsized in December
OL,18,F2022.
