OL,7,FOn Monday, the pilot of that boat,
OL,8,FIbrahima Bah, of four passengers who
OL,9,Fdrowned.
OL,11,FBah, from Senegal and over 18, was
OL,12,Fcharged with four counts of
OL,13,Fmanslaughter and one count of piloting
OL,14,Fto facilitate illegal entry into the
OL,15,FUK from France on 14 December 2022.
OL,17,FHowever Hamza believes Bah's actions
OL,18,Fsaved his life.
