OL,7,FHe said "Everyone was scared. Since
OL,8,Fthe boat was too small there wasn't
OL,9,Fenough space for everybody"
OL,11,F"When they turned on the engine again,
OL,12,Fthe boat was driving fast and I
OL,13,Fbelieve the guy that you just named
OL,14,F(Bah) saved many people's lives. If he
OL,15,Fwasn't there, there would be the
OL,16,Fpossibility that more people would've
OL,17,Fdrowned and died"
