OL,7,FBah previously told the court how he
OL,8,Fwas trying to come to the UK to claim
OL,9,Fasylum, when people smugglers offered
OL,10,Ffree travel for him and a close friend
OL,11,Fif he piloted the boat.
OL,13,FBut when he reached the shore and saw
OL,14,Fthe state of the dinghy, he says he
OL,15,Fchanged his mind.
OL,17,FBah claims the traffickers then
OL,18,Fthreatened to kill him if he didn't.
