OL,7,FHamza, who worked for the military
OL,8,Fback home, said he felt intimidated by
OL,9,Fthe gang.
OL,11,F"The smugglers were wearing masks and
OL,12,Fit was impossible for us to see them.
OL,14,F"They were equipped with so many
OL,15,Fweapons and I was really afraid and
OL,16,Fscared for my life, because they were
OL,17,Freally frightening people."
